      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, im planning a solo trip to chicago next month and i'm kinda nervous about navigating the city alone. i'm looking for a neighborhood that feels really safe, upscale, and has a good sense of community? also, given everything going on lately, which areas should i probably avoid so i dont run into any trouble?",
