    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the tips. i noticed people talking online about certain parts of the south side or even parts of the west side being kinda 'sketchy' or high-risk. is that actually something i should worry about as a solo traveler? like, are there specific blocks or types of neighborhoods in those areas that i should just steer clear of entirely?",
